{"tid":158521,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"Hsbc打電話黎要我用英文傾計…?","createTime":"2017-03-16T10:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T10:47:43.000Z","uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10411a71d976e3640b086911e8a2956e0a1913f2","tid":158521,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:29:51.000Z","msg":"今日返緊工做緊野果陣突然電話響 一聽就係英文 聽口音係外國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對方up得出我個全名 自稱來自hsbc 我開頭覺得係騙案 問返佢點解會搵我<br />\n佢大概話我上年年中報過一份hsbc job 所以有我記錄 佢唔講我都醒唔起我大半年前報過hsbc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後佢類似話有另一份job 想同我傾下計先<br />\n我問佢係咩job  但我英文差加上我做野環境有人聲所以聽得唔清楚 我又唔想認低威 於是用簡單英文答佢話依加做緊野唔方便傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />約左聽日再傾<br />\n有冇人有過類似經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d11e6503d18ded638d908ad33a569545359495","tid":158521,"uid":60195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:37:38.000Z","msg":"Hsbc 請人個part outsource外 係會有外國人打黎 <br />\n照傾啦"},{"pid":"c970a0a17688043b434eb523b3677df2ad958317","tid":158521,"uid":74846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:40:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我咁耐以黎搵工都雞腸架喎<br />\n屌你我連二手交收啲人都全用英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但明明出到黎係講廣東話既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸:雞腸唔好"},{"pid":"83f6a5ac7beebbf71450e1dbd099c056841900c6","tid":158521,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:47:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我咁耐以黎搵工都雞腸架喎<br />\n屌你我連二手交收啲人都全用英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但明明出到黎係講廣東話既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸:雞腸唔好</blockquote><br />\n見工要用全英文我未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（廢人搵廢工）同埋我對住外國人會驚d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb4b5ad0bf6af099a6d7a73395c4f692df30676","tid":158521,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:47:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hsbc 請人個part outsource外 係會有外國人打黎 <br />\n照傾啦</blockquote><br />\n哦 原來係正常程序"}]}